e;"></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-bottom: -12px;margin-left: 6px;outline: 0px;width: 27px;visibility: visible;"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 334.6 286.9" style="visibility: visible;"><polygon style="fill: rgb(245, 202, 70);visibility: visible;" points="334.6,286.9 185.3,286.9 185.3,0.4 334.6,150.4 "></polygon><polygon style="fill: none;stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width: 6;stroke-miterlimit: 10;visibility: visible;" points="147.6,283.9 3.3,283.9 3.3,7.4 147.6,150.4 "></polygon></svg></section><section style="padding-top: 20px;padding-right: 25px;padding-left: 11px;outline: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 253, 244);visibility: visible;text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">“歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">”全身涂满黑漆，惊现美军基地，里面还坐着白人飞行员，如此怪异一幕，解放军看了却不动声色。</span></span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="369" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.6660649819494585" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTfdkXPnficWzMp3EQibmyJoCLg3IOwNYUDGeov545kJ7QXJlxxf8Qr0xpKgyTQFibt6qZqBAVrxrTrA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">前言：随着中国军事力量快速崛起，美国军方的敏感神经也被紧紧牵动着，不仅由衷感慨解放军的发展之快速，高精尖武器之先进，同时又难以摘下有色眼镜，多次贬低解放军，傲慢与偏见在美军身上显示的淋漓尽致，在涉华问题上，也总做出一些自相矛盾的事，尽管如此，有些事美军还是不得不承认。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">接下来，让我们一起看一下，出现在美军基地的黑色“歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>”，是什么来头，未来是否对解放军形成威慑？<p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;">01</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;visibility: visible;"><p style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;visibility: visible;"> <strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">黑色“歼<span style="font-family: Calibri;">20</span>”，惊现美基地</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 196px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-indent: 0em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;visibility: visible;">   </span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;">   </span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 196px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-indent: 0em;font-family: Calibri;text-align: justify;visibility: visible;"> </span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">据悉，6月19日到6月25日，巴黎举办了第54届巴黎-布里歇国际航空航天展览会。这是自2021年航展取消以来，两年内的首次航展活动，因此，该活动吸引了全球不少知名航空公司的参加。比如波音、达索、空客、洛克希德·马丁、巴西航空工业以及中国航空工业等，大概有30万游客参观，可以说，本届巴黎航展是有史以来最大规模的国际航展。</span></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><br></section><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">据美媒消息称，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">在美国本土的北卡罗来纳州的美陆战队基地，出现了一架“歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">隐身战斗机”</span></span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">，</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">该机全身被涂成了黑色，尾翼上还有红色五星标志，消息一出，网友顿时炸开了锅，美军基地为何会出现一架“歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">”呢？</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">从一些现场照片分析来看，这架“歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>”其实是一架全尺寸的模型，外形设计以及涂装也不是最新款歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>该有的设计，更像是<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">10</span>年前刚刚问世的歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>原型机，那么，大费周章弄一个模型机出来，美军是打算干什么呢？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="308" data-backw="553" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.5569620253164557" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTfdkXPnficWzMp3EQibmyJoCXAtRhI60USxGf4Ay6a0ACI5UZXrIc2PUicX3Vf0IM7QNO2o48Hb47hA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="553" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">美国消息人士指出，这很有可能是用来充当陆战队飞行员的“教具”，培训“目视与传感器”任务，简单来说，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">就是让飞行员更加熟悉歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">外形特性，以来在空中“偶遇”时，不会显得措手不及，正所谓“知己知彼百战不怠”。</span></span></strong></span></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1698305995177" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1698305995177"></mpcpc><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">毕竟，这些年随着歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>战斗效能的不断提升，已经引起美军高度警惕，尤其是在“中国威胁”紧张情绪的渲染下，美军内部普遍认为，未来歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>将成为解放军空军的主力，所以，在日常训练中将歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>作为假想敌，一定程度上可以帮助美军在应对歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>时更加从容。<p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">02</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.5pt;"> </span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">美军假想敌，从俄罗斯转向中国</span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 160px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">值得注意的是，这并不是美军第一次拿假想敌飞机来进行训练了。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">冷战时期，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">为了对抗苏联等国的作战飞机编队，美军还专门成立了假想敌中队</span></strong></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，为了让这个假想敌更加逼真，还大费周章从各种渠道弄来了“真机”，还涂上了对手涂装与美军一同参与训练，旨在增强美军在实战中应对假想敌的能力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="310" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.5595667870036101" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTfdkXPnficWzMp3EQibmyJoC5iahpicN3GnZzJJUH85ibTciau2YSh0267RnwMVXicW3ZTeDibSBicX6ntQpA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">直到后来，冷战结束，苏联也随之解体，一时间称王称霸的美军直接搞来了苏<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">27</span>等数架先进战机，以提高假想敌中队的实力，进一步帮助美军提升应对作战能力。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">苏联解体后，美国的最大假想敌一直是俄罗斯，在军事、战略等领域中，都在与俄罗斯针锋相对，然而，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">随着中国军事力量的崛起，美国的假想敌从俄罗斯更多的转向中国，</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">尤其是歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">问世后，更让一向傲慢的美军感受到了前所未有的挫败感。</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">所以，此次美军打造出“歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>”模型机，让飞行员观摩并制定战术，也不算奇怪，从某种程度上来说，此举也让华盛顿的谎言，不攻自破。<p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">03</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="margin-left: 0pt;outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"> <strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">被模仿的，不止歼<span style="font-family: Calibri;">20</span></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"></strong></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">JF-22超高速风洞的应用<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">美国觊觎三峡大坝已久</span></span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">中国“杀手”卫星有多强，美航母无处遁形</span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"> </span></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;"><br></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">综合报道来看，美军对解放军歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>战机的态度，十分纠结，在一些公开场合，他们一贯贬低歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>，即使曾在东海上空遭遇歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>拦截，也认为这款战机不足为惧，与美军战机相比，完全没有任何打赢的可能性，算不上势均力敌的对手。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">但在私底下，美军却对歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">殚精竭虑，不仅在假想敌中队中添加了针对歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">的科目，还造出了全尺寸模型机，由此说明，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">的实力在美军眼中值得警惕，必须让飞行员在目视范围内，学会辨别解放军这款五代机。</span></span></strong></span></span><strong style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="330" data-backw="553" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.596745027124774" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTfdkXPnficWzMp3EQibmyJoCoqoggR7KYeictX4PIT2iazrFuPLWK40qn5l7s9IRRvvXJ6C5SY8cEmiaA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="553" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">有消息称，从冷战时期到如今，美军一直都非常重视假想敌中队的战略作用，模拟过的战斗机除了俄军苏<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">27</span>，还有苏<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">30</span>、苏<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">57</span>等机型，还有中国的歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">10</span>、歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">16</span>机型都曾在这个假想敌中队中出现过。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2017</span>年，美军就计划从瑞典引进“鹰狮”战斗机，装备美军假想敌中队用于模拟中国歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">10</span>战机，还曾把自己的<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">F18</span>战机刷上与歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">16</span>相似的涂装，用于进行一些科目演习。</span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1698305987484" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1698305987484"></mpcpc><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">从美空军假想敌中队中主要模拟机型来看，大部分都是中俄最新型战机</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，由此可见，起码在未来几十年，中俄都会成为美军的“眼中钉”，制定一揽子针对性战术，以寻求巩固美式霸权的绝对存在。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">04</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="margin-left: 0pt;outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"> </span></strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">假想敌中队作用，遭网友质疑</span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">中国海军的快速发展</span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">值得注意的是，美国假想敌中队中的机型，不仅仅是模仿一个涂装这么简单。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">他们会让美军飞行员先熟悉他国战机的外形特点，随后会让美军自己驾驶的战机，全方位模拟他国战机的飞行特点和机动性能等，以此可锤炼美军飞行员的实战对抗能力。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">上述提到</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，美军曾引进瑞典“鹰狮”战机模拟歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，就是因为这两款战机采用的都是单发、鸭翼设计的战斗机，有很多相似之处。</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="516" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.9314079422382672" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTfdkXPnficWzMp3EQibmyJoCR0oG1KxFlHPxwJx7DXAOiaMPXmCiaGNS1oAX4tCatNIyOHKOf3MpKiaLg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">不难看出，用专业的假想敌中队对于美国空军的帮助有多大，这不仅仅是美军飞行员日常训练的一部分，同时也是美军全面备战的一部分，尤其是在如今这个国际形势下，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">美军一直在为潜在战争冲突做着全面准备。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"></span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">不过，这种战备工作看起来十分缜密，实际上存在很大的漏洞。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">就比如此次出现在美军基地的黑色“歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>”，我们只在早期几个原型机上用过，后期的几架原型机以及正式列装的歼<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span>，采用的都是低可视涂装。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">此前，美军一架</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-8A</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">巡逻机在南海上空“作妖”，就遭到解放军战机驱离，但他们却将苏</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">35</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">战机错认为歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">11</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，这两款战机虽然外形相似，但涂装有很大俄区别，不少网友质疑，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">一线美军飞行员连这点辨别能力都没有，假想敌中队忙活了这么些年，就这点成就吗？</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">结语：关于美军基地出现的黑色“歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">”，大家还有什么了解的吗？欢迎在评论区留下您的看法和故事。</span></span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"></span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.5pt;"><p></p></span></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(255, 76, 65);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>点亮【在看】，持续关注更多精彩内容</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="540049346" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
